    <description>The Payments &amp; Credits serves as a vital record capturing payments made against individual invoices. Users can specify whether the payment was made in cash or as an offset against other outstanding amounts.
When loaded via Payment Studio, these records are automatically created with an approved status and associated with individual invoices upon Payment Studio record approval.
Population Requirement Details: Conditionally Required if legacy data loading is required and is not loaded via payment studio
[MODULE: Finance]
[LOAD: Yes]
[PREREQUISITES: If the Payment Type (Payment/Credit field) equals Cash Payment, Invoice, Payment on Account. If the Payment Type (Payment/Credit field) is not equal to &#39;Cash Payment&#39; then the below are required., Invoice, Letter of Credit, Payable, Security Deposit, Credit Memo]
[REPLACEMENT OBJECT API: NA]
[COMMENTS: NA]</description>
